creator: Samuel Taylor Coleridge
description:
LibriVox recording of Answer to a Child's Question by Samuel Taylor Coleridge.
Read in English by Anna Gouldsmith; CaprishaPage; Diana Majlinger; Drew Johnson; David Lawrence; Deena Rhoads; dsilber01; Ernst Pattynama; Jonathan Andersen; Jayes; Jason Mills; Jennifer Dorr; Jannie Meisberger; Kara Shallenberg; Kimberly Dion; Lee Ann Howlett; Leonard Wilson; Pat David; Pam Castille; ravenotation; Anastasiia Solokha

LibriVox volunteers bring you 21 recordings of Answer to a Child's Question by Samuel Taylor Coleridge. This was the Weekly Poetry project for October 6, 2013. (Summary by Diana Majlinger)

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

M4B Format Available
